Royal Dutch Shell

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

"Shell Company" redirects here. It is not to be confused with Shell corporation.

Royal Dutch Shell plc





Headquarters in The Hague, Netherlands




Type

